name: Karie Neth
Lore: 'Gray Squadron 2''s gunner at the Battle of Endor. Member of Rogue Squadron. Replaced Bothan pilot lost during secret mission ordered by Rebel command staff.',
Text: 'Adds 2 to power of anything she pilots. While aboard your starship, adds 1 to each of its weapon destiny draws (2 if Gray Squadron 2 or when with Telsij).',
